      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "SUBJECT: Project \"SIGN\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "Gentlemen:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "Accompanying this letter is a small sample of soil. This",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "soil was taken from a depression reputed to have been caused",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "by a \"flying saucer\" described as being approximately two feet",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "in diameter and one foot thick which supposedly settled gently",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "to the ground, rebounded to a height of about twenty feet and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "then continued on its journey. Although the declivity was immedi-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "ately covered by a large washtub a heavy rain subsequently filled",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "dirt could be taken.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "the depression about one/third full of water before any sample of",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "In an effort to approach this incident objectively to deter-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "mine every possible clue, it has been deemed advisable to have",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "this soil sample analyzed and tested. Upon inquiry, your Dayton",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "representative stated that the FBI Laboratory would accomplish",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "the required tests.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "RECORDED - 1 63-83894-146",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "It is the desire of this Headquarters to ascertain, in parti-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "cular, if there are traces of unusual Elements or Alloys adhering",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "to the surface of the particles, or if any abnormality in structure",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "exists showing that the soil was subjected to intense heat, gases",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "or radio-active substances, etc. Unfortunately, in this regard,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "no one thought to forward a sample of the soil surrounding the de-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "pression so no comparison of soils can be made at this time. Should",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "the subsequent test show anything unusual some arrangement could be",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "made to procure some of the surrounding soil so that a comparative",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "analysis could be made. The accompanying sample has not been test-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "ed by any other agency, nor will it be.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
